<h3>Insert Data Into "Products"</h3>
<p>Insert into Products table and view entire products table. This functionality is for business use only.
    Important: The number used for "Vendor ID" must exist as "Vendor ID" in the Vendors table prior to use in this insert.
    To see all Vendor ID's, go to Vendors page. If desired vendor does not exist yet, add it.
    Additionally, the "Link" attribute refers to a designated path to album art which exists in the "public" folder.
    Thus, for testing purposes, it is unimportant what goes in that text box.
</p>
<form action="flip3.engr.oregonstate.edu:7755/products_insert" method="GET">
    <label for="vid">Vendor ID: </label>
    <input type="text" id="vid"><br>
    <label for="title">Album Title: </label>
    <input type="text" id="title"><br>
    <label for="artist">Artist: </label>
    <input type="text" id="artist"><br>
    <label for="genre">Genre: </label>
    <input type="text" id="genre"><br>
    <label for="year">Year: </label>
    <input type="text" id="year"><br>
    <label for="stock">Stock: </label>
    <input type="text" id="stock"><br>
    <label for="price">Price: </label>
    <input type="text" id="price"><br>
    <label for="link">Link: </label>
    <input type="text" id="link"><br>
    <input type="submit" id="products">
</form>

<div>
    <table>
        <thead>
            <tr id="head">
                <th>Product ID</th>
                <th>Vendor ID</th>
                <th>Album Title</th>
                <th>Artist</th>
                <th>Genre</th>
                <th>Year</th>
                <th>Stock</th>
                <th>Price</th>
                <th>Update</th>
                <th>Delete</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody id="table">
             {{#each results}}
            <tr>
                <td>{{this.pid}}</td>
                <td>{{this.vid}}</td>
                <td>{{this.title}}</td>
                <td>{{this.artist}}</td>
                <td>{{this.genre}}</td>
                <td>{{this.year}}</td>
                <td>{{this.stock}}</td>
                <td>{{this.price}}</td>
                <td><button type="button" class="delete_button">Delete</button></td>
            </tr>
            {{/each}}
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>

